        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="4396.159" end="x">Here is a question—rather a maybe leading question. A few weeks ago in a British paper I saw a quarter-of-a-page ad to trying to recruit soldiers for the service in Palestine. It had a headline: "It is a man's job."</span>
